Introduction

Dita is an Indonesian singer and the first one from her country to enter the K-pop industry.

Best known for being a former member of the girl group SECRET NUMBER, she debuted on May 19, 2020, with the single album “Who Dis?”

On April 4, 2025, she, alongside members Jinny and Minji, released a collective statement announcing their departures from the group as well as Vine Entertainment.
